Step To Create 2gp Package
1. Retrieve your code in Vs code
2. sfdx force:auth:web:login -d -a DevhubLite      // DevhubLite is alias
3. sf package create --name "Name of the package" --package-type Managed --path force-app --target-dev-hub DevhubLite
4. sf package version create --package "Name of the package" --code-coverage --installation-key-bypass  --wait 10 -v DevhubLite        // --codecoverage you can check 8 time in a days    --skip-ancestor-check
5. To check coverage before creating package sf package version report --package "Id of package" --verbose    
5. To create Release use this sf package version promote --package Id of package


