Auth Partner devhub
sf force:auth:web:login -d -a <aliase_name>

To check All apex text classed
sf apex run test --test-level RunLocalTests --wait 10

Create Beta Package:
sf package version create --package "Package Name" --code-coverage --installation-key-bypass  --wait 10 -v aliase_name

For Patch Version:
sf package version create --package "Package Name" --version-number 1.2.0.NEXT --patch --code-coverage

below command to promote to package
sf package version promote --package <Beta_Package_Id>




For Push Upgrade For All:
sf package push-upgrade schedule --package <Package_ID>

Push Upgrade for One Org:
sf package push-upgrade schedule --package <Package_ID> --org-list <ORG_ID>

After Push Check Status:
sf package push-upgrade list --target-dev-hub yourDevHubAlias
sf package push-upgrade report --push-upgrade-id <Pass-Id-Here> --target-dev-hub yourDevHubAlias

